{"article_id":"tZLFNHZHQgsVfBBg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Supreme Court revived President Trump ' s extreme vetting travel ban Monday ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"ruling","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that much of it can go into effect","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"- and along the way delivering an implicit rebuke to the army of lower-court judges","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"who blasted the president as anti-Muslim .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"In a unanimous unsigned ruling , the justices said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"the president has important national security powers","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that the courts must respect","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and ruled","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that he likely has the power","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"to deny entry to broad categories of would-be visitors and immigrants .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"But the justices said","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"those","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"who already have a connection to the U.S.","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"- either a job offer , an admission to an educational program or a close family connection -","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"will be exempted from the 90-day ban on travel from six countries as well as the 120-day pause on refugees .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Minutes after the ruling , both sides were fighting over what that meant .","depth":3},{"id":17,"text":"The president said","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"his plans will \" become largely effective \"","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"and called the ruling \" a clear victory for our national security . \"","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"\" My number one responsibility as Commander in Chief is to keep the American people safe , \"","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"\" Today ' s ruling allows me to use an important tool","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"for protecting our Nation ' s homeland .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"I am also particularly gratified","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"that the Supreme Court ' s decision was 9-0 . \"","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"Stung by denial ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"gun rights advocates vow to bring other concealed carry cases before Supreme Court","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Some took an optimistic approach ,","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"approval of the exemptions will prevent few visitors from entering the U.S. under either the travel ban or the refugee pause .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Others were outraged","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"that the court gave an imprimatur to any of the president ' s policy .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"The Homeland Security Department said","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"it will soon issue guidance","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"about how it will carry out the court ' s directives .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"Advocacy groups said","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"they will be watching closely","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and will be prepared to file lawsuits","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"if they think","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"the government is refusing entry to deserving visitors , refugees and immigrants .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" This order allows only a narrow sliver of the ban to go forward .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"We will stop any attempt by the Trump administration","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"to go further , \"","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"said Omar C. Jadwat , director of the Immigrant Rights Project at the American Civil Liberties Union .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"The court has set oral arguments on the full case for October ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"when the next term begins .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"But all the justices Monday signaled a reluctance","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"to follow the lead of several lower courts ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"which said","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s campaign rhetoric regarding Muslims","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"poisoned his executive orders .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"During the presidential campaign , Mr. Trump proposed a full ban on admitting any Muslims to the U.S .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"In January ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"after taking office ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"he issued an executive order","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that imposed a 120-day pause on all new refugees ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"dropped the annual ceiling of refugees to 50,000","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"- down from the 110,000","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"that President Obama had set ,","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"and called for a 90-day halt in admissions from Iran , Iraq , Libya , Somalia , Sudan , Syria and Yemen .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Those seven countries","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"- all predominantly Muslim -","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"had been first identified by Congress and Mr. Obama as so terror-prone and dangerous","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"that their citizens needed extra vetting .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"After courts ruled against the January executive order ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Mr. Trump issued a revised order in March","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"removing Iraq from the targeted countries","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"and allowing waivers","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"that granted admission to people","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"who","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"the government deemed","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"already had connections to the U.S. , such as an approved visa or family","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"living in the country .","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"Some legal analysts said","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"the Supreme Court ruling did little more than codify that latest policy .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"\" An American individual or entity","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"that has a bona fide relationship with a particular person","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"seeking to enter the country as a refugee","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"can legitimately claim concrete hardship","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"if that person is excluded , \"","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"the justices said in the unsigned opinion .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"\" But","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"when it comes to refugees","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"who lack any such connection to the United States , for the reasons","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"we have set out ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"the balance tips in favor of the Government ' s compelling need","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"to provide for the Nation ' s security . \"","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"Three members of the court","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"- Justices Clarence Thomas , Samuel A. Alito Jr. and Neil M. Gorsuch -","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"issued their own opinion","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"they would have gone further","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"and upheld the president ' s entire policy .","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"\" I fear","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"that the Court ' s remedy will prove unworkable , \"","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"said Justice Thomas ,","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"writing for the dissenters .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"the decision creates a nightmare for the administration ,","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"which must come up with definitions","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"of what constitutes \" sufficient connection . \"","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"The court also created an exemption to Mr. Trump ' s 50,000-refugee cap ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that anyone already in the pipeline with close connections to the U.S. must be admitted - a striking move","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"that garnered little explanation in the 13-page ruling .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"Some advocacy groups argued","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"that meant no refugees will be blocked","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"because of the ban ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"because everyone in the pipeline already has ties to the U.S. by dint of the fact","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"that a resettlement agency in the U.S. is working on their case .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Other groups feared","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that some refugees will be left on the outside and stranded in dangerous conditions .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"Those future fights aside , the ruling is the first major legal victory for Mr. Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"who had been blasted by lower courts","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"- chiefly Democratic-appointed judges -","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"for showing \" animus \" to Muslims","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"and for failing to justify his national security concerns .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"The justices , though , said","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"the president deserves deference","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"when acting on national security concerns in immigration matters ,","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"where Congress has given the executive branch significant leeway .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"\" The Supreme Court did what the lower court judges would not :","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"treat President Trump like any other president with the ' presumption of regularity , ' \"","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"Josh Blackman , associate professor at South Texas College of Law in Houston , wrote on his blog .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"\" The justices did not delve into the president ' s Twitter account ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"nor did they parse his campaign statements . \"","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"The justices did , however , signal","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"that they expect Mr. Trump to use the reprieve","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"to quickly figure out and put into place new vetting policies","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"- which was the point of the temporary pauses in the first place ,","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"according to the administration .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"\" Given the Government ' s representations in this litigation","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"concerning the resources","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"required to complete the 20-day review ,","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"we fully expect","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"that the relief","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"we grant today","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"will permit the Executive to conclude its internal work","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"and provide adequate notice to foreign governments \" within the time frame","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"laid out by Mr. Trump ,","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"the justices said .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"That could make much of the case moot by October ,","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"when the next session of the court begins .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":289,"left":170,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":161,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":160,"right":16,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":149,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":0,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":146,"right":147,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":147,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":154,"right":158,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":151,"right":153,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":5,"right":150,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":8,"right":152,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":9,"right":10,"relati